A very fat man decided to lose weight. I've tried everything, all the diets, but there's no result. I saw an ad in the newspaper: lose 20 kg in one day! He called and was told that a specialist would come to the house.
The next day, the doorbell rings, the man opens, and there stands a tall, slender, naked blonde and says:
- If you catch up with me, I'm yours!
I chased for several hours, caught, fucked a blonde, gets on the scales and 20 kg as if nothing had happened. He calls again on the same ad and says:
- I want to lose another 40 kg.
They answer him:
- Okay, wait for tomorrow.
The next day, the doorbell rings, the man opens and sees a hefty, two-meter-tall bully who says to the man:
- If I catch up with you, you're mine!
